2013-01-01 transaction 1
  1                                             $1
  1:2                                          $-1

3000-01-02 transaction 2
  1                                             $1
  1:2:3                                        $-1

test bal --flat
                $ 1.0  1
               $ -1.0  1:2
 --------------------
                    0
stderr
warning: there are transactions dated after --at
end test

